## ğŸš€ Project Overview  
The **Salesforce Business Finance & Investment Tracker** is a cloud-based solution built on Salesforce to help **small & medium-sized businesses (SMBs)** manage their **financial operations, investments, and cash flow** in one centralized system.  

Instead of relying on scattered spreadsheets and manual processes, this project provides **real-time dashboards, automation, and role-based access** for CFOs, finance teams, and auditors.  

---

## ğŸ›  Features  
- **Financial Data Centralization** â€“ Track income, expenses, invoices, and vendor payments.  
- **Accounts Receivable & Payable** â€“ Manage outstanding invoices and due dates.  
- **Investment Tracking** â€“ Monitor returns from FDs, mutual funds, equities, or bonds.  
- **Cash Flow Dashboards** â€“ Real-time visibility of inflows, outflows, and reserves.  
- **Goal-Based Planning** â€“ Align financial decisions with business expansion goals.  
- **Automation** â€“ Invoice reminders, recurring expense tracking, and compliance alerts.  
- **Role-Based Access** â€“ CFO, Finance Managers, Accountants, and Auditors with specific permissions.  

